==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔː(r)mən|-ɔː(r)mən]]

===Noun===
'''Mormon'''  (''plural:'' '''Mormons''')

# A person who belongs to one of the [[Christian]] religous groups related to the religion founded by [[w:Joseph Smith, Jr.|Joseph Smith, Jr.]].  This religion founded by Joseph Smith Jr., is known as The [[Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints]].
# The ancient American [[prophet]] of Mormon theology who translated the [[Book of Mormon]] written in reformed egyptian.

